msgstr "ເລືອກວິທີການຊຳລະເງິນເພື່ອຊຳລະຍອດຄ້າງຊຳລະ"

#. module: pos_settle_due
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/pos_settle_due/static/src/overrides/components/partner_list/partner_line/partner_line.xml:0
